When your device’s Location setting is turned on and High Accuracy or Battery Saving mode is selected, your device uses Google’s location service to provide location information.

You can turn this on or off at any time in the Google Settings app. This doesn't affect this device's ability to send the information it needs to receive essential services such as system updates and security."
